# TraderRank Pro

Monorepo: `frontend/` (Next.js 15), `backend/` (NestJS + Prisma), `mt5-guard/` (Expo), `local-admin/`.

## Stack

Next.js 15 · NestJS · PostgreSQL (Neon) · JWT/OAuth/wallet auth · NOWPayments USDT · Render deploy

## Key paths

| Area | Path |
|------|------|
| API modules | `backend/src/<feature>/` |
| Pages | `frontend/src/app/` |
| Schema | `backend/prisma/schema.prisma` |
| Support KB | `backend/src/ai/knowledge/platform-knowledge.md` |
| Webhooks | `docs/TRADE_WEBHOOK.md`, `docs/SIGNAL_INGEST_API.md` |

## Non-obvious business rules

- KYC required for **payouts only** — not registration or signal submit
- Payout split: **40% trader / 60% platform**
- Virtual account: $1K start, 5% risk per trade, Bronze → Elite tiers
- Prisma uses **`db push`** — no migration files
- Registration payment (or promo) required for **ACTIVE** status

